com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class GetXrefForEffectiveDateRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianRequest
      • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianObjectRequest
        • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.GetXrefForEffectiveDateRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordKeyProvider, SiperianObjectUidProvider, Serializable

    public class GetXrefForEffectiveDateRequest
extends SiperianObjectRequest
implements RecordKeyProvider

    Retrieves a list of xref records for the specified BO rowid object, effective date and history Date. Also can retrieves the other records for all the other periods except the one that include the effective date Get API supports data filtering.

    Required Parameters:

    • SiperianObjectUid - the type and the name of the package, base object to be queried.
    • setRecordKey(RecordKey) - Specifies the key of the record that needs to be retrieved.
    Optional Parameters:

    • Effective Date - the date used to retrieve an effective period of the BO.
    • History Date - The history date for wich the request is executed
    Author:
    lchikkak
